#name
Brander
#req
goats, sheeps, pigs, horses or cows and (optional) branch
#text
This bot brands your animals. In order to brand animals, you need a kindled brand. You can build a kiln and place an area with a fire (branch or candelabrum).In this case, you will need fuel for the kiln. Sticks are used as fuel.You should also select the type of animals located in the relevant area(goats, sheeps, pigs, horses or cows).